Dependencies-dev: libchimeratk-controlsystemadapter-dev dev-doocs-clientlib dev-doocs-serverlib

Description-dev: Header and cmake files for the DOOCS Adapter for the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter. The files you need to compile against libchimeratk-controlsystemadaper-doocsadapter.
Description-lib: libchimeratk-controlsystemadapter-doocsadapter provides the DOOCS Adapter for the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter. Linking against this library will make a DOOCS server out of any control application built against the ChimeraTK ControlSystemAdapter.

